title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 7 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 7 2022
description:
Climate wackos of the Biden Regime want you to pay record-high gas prices. Democrat Sen. Debbie Stabenow says she doesn't care about high gas prices because she drives an electric car. L.A.-based radio show host John Phillips talks with Clay and Buck about the political earthquake brewing in California. WSJ writer describes miserable EV road trip.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
